name: BARGAIN BIN
description:
This is a Bargain Bin of all Stage 1 damaged/factory seconds or old garments.

Stage 1 damaged consists of either: Small holes, stains/burns or faded/damaged prints.

By purchasing one of these items you accept the below terms:
- You are not able to return the product
- You understand that products may have minor damage to them, which is mentioned in each description
- Items may or may not contain hem labels/neck size stamping.
- Most or all of these products are made from our old materials and not our new, high-tech production machines, meaning they are of less quality and will not last as long.

ALL ITEMS ARE AT AN EXTREMELY REDUCED PRICE.
